         <abstract id="aspace_905eaf41363c26fc2003f9ae95d50e8d">The collection consists of miscellaneous memorabilia of Vance R. Dittman, Jr. (Yale 1924). Also included are creative works by Catherine Pierson Dittman (wife of Vance Dittman), who studied painting at Yale, and Dean B. Lyman.</abstract>
    
